data.name: GetReference
desc: specifies service of a reference field.

properties.name: CurrentPresentation
desc: contains the current content of the text field.
This property is especially useful for import/export purposes.

properties.name: ReferenceFieldLanguage
desc: contains the language id of the alternative language-dependent references.
Alternative language-dependent forms of reference types.
The current set of supported languages is:

properties.name: ReferenceFieldPart
desc: contains the type of the reference.

properties.name: ReferenceFieldSource
desc: contains the source of the reference.

properties.name: SequenceNumber
desc: contains the sequence number of a set expression field that is used as sequence field or the value of the ReferenceId property of a footnote or endnote.

properties.name: SourceName
desc: contains the name of the source.
Depending on the property ReferenceFieldSource it may be the name of a bookmark, a reference mark.
